{
  "texts": [
    "As AI becomes more integrated into daily life and crucial decision making tasks, establishing trust in AI is essential.",
    "This necessitates a focus on enhancing transparency, explainability, fairness, and robustness within AI systems, which is also central to trustworthy AI.",
    "While AI represents a new generation of automation technology with unique characteristics, research on trust in earlier forms of automation remains relevant.",
    "This historical perspective can inform the development of trust in AI by highlighting the important trust factors.",
    "Incorporating lessons from the past, the transition to AI additionally demands a renewed focus on ethical considerations, transparency, and user engagement to foster a deeper and more comprehensive trust."
  ]
}